<p>You expect the owner/proprietor to give you a discount for&nbsp;the use of your&nbsp;energy you already purchased and stored<strong> or&nbsp;are you giving your energy&nbsp;away for free in order&nbsp;for someone to accept&nbsp;your&nbsp;"digital currency"?</strong> Why would they&nbsp;go through these machinations&nbsp;when everyone standing right behind you has&nbsp;recognized, acceptable money,&nbsp;known in the real world,&nbsp;in the real or black markets?</p>
