<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-3334533">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Sat, 03/16/2013 - 01:13 | <a href="/news/2013-03-15/guest-post-what-world-bitcoin#comment-3334533" class="active">3334533</a></span>
              <b><a href="/users/bunga-bunga" title="View user profile.">Bunga Bunga</a></b>
